column8: Cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of a shower, most likely this morning. Winds southerly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the evening.

Partly cloudy. The chance of fog in the early morning. Medium (40%) chance of light showers. Light winds becoming southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then tending southerly in the middle of the day.
The chance of morning fog. Mostly sunny afternoon. Light winds becoming south to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Light winds becoming southerly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Humid. Partly cloudy. The chance of morning fog. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. The chance of a thunderstorm later in the day. Light winds.

Humid. Cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm. Winds north to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h increasing to 35 km/h before shifting south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the day.
Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers. Winds southerly 20 to 30 km/h turning southwesterly during the morning.
